<div class="ui welcome message">
  <h1>Welcome to AAF Identity Enhancement</h1>

  <p>
    You were invited by <strong><%= @invitation.provider.name %></strong>, so
    that they can enhance your identity for access to online services.
  </p>

  <p>
    Your invitation has <strong>already been accepted</strong>, so you no longer
    require the invitation link from the original email. If you arrived here
    from a bookmark, you should update your bookmark after clicking the button
    below.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you did not accept your invitation, please send a copy of your invitation
    email to <a href="mailto:support@aaf.edu.au">support@aaf.edu.au</a> and we
    will investigate.
  </p>

  <div class="line-of-buttons">
    <%= button_link_to(dashboard_path, class: 'massive blue icon') do -%>
      <%= icon_tag('angle double right') %>
      View Dashboard
    <%- end -%>
  </div>
</div>
